pt"> m</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">odel</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">s of</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> public service</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">s</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> delivery</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">, and provides evidence of </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">local </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">innovation when meaningful decentralisation has been exercised. </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">Greater </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">Manchester</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">’s City Deal </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">Earnback </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">mechanism </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">proposes </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">to </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">generate </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">growth through infrast</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">ructure investment and </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">then </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">return</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> a share of the </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">‘</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">proceeds of growth</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">’</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> (through higher tax takes and </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">a lower benefits bill</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">) back to the City Region.</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-f